sequenceDiagram
    participant Ca as Cashier
    participant POS as React POS Frontend
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant IS as Inventory Service
    participant CS as Customer Service
    
    Ca->>POS: Search medicine
    POS->>API: GET /api/medicines/search?q=paracetamol
    API->>DB: Query medicines
    DB-->>API: Medicine list with stock
    API-->>POS: Search results
    POS-->>Ca: Display medicines
    
    Ca->>POS: Add to cart (qty: 2)
    Note over POS: Cart stored in local state
    
    Ca->>POS: Enter customer phone
    POS->>API: GET /api/customers?phone=0771234567
    API->>DB: Find customer
    DB-->>API: Customer data (loyalty: 150 pts)
    API-->>POS: Customer details
    POS-->>Ca: Show loyalty discount (5% off)
    
    Ca->>POS: Process payment (Cash)
    POS->>API: POST /api/sales (Begin Transaction)
    
    API->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    API->>IS: Check stock availability
    IS->>DB: Query inventory (FIFO)
    DB-->>IS: Available batches
    IS-->>API: Stock confirmed
    
    API->>DB: Create Sale record
    API->>DB: Create SaleItems
    API->>IS: Update inventory (deduct stock)
    IS->>DB: UPDATE inventory (FIFO)
    
    API->>CS: Update loyalty points (+20 pts)
    CS->>DB: UPDATE customers SET loyalty_points = 170
    
    API->>DB: Check low stock threshold
    alt Stock below minimum
        API->>DB: Create notification (Low Stock Alert)
    end
    
    API->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
    API-->>POS: Sale successful (Invoice ID: 12345)
    
    POS->>API: GET /api/sales/12345/invoice
    API-->>POS: Invoice PDF
    POS-->>Ca: Print invoice
    Ca-->>Customer: Hand over medicine & invoice
    
    Note over Ca,Customer: Transaction time: < 1 minute
